titles.title: A resolution authorizing the printing with illustrations of a document entitled "Committee on Appropriations, United States Senate, 126th Anniversary, 1867-1993".

vote.text: Resolution agreed to in Senate without amendment by Voice Vote. (consideration: CR 11/18/93 S16209)

bill.summary: 11/18/1993--Introduced. Authorizes the printing as a Senate document of a compilation of materials entitled "Committee on Appropriations, United States Senate, 126th Anniversary, 1867-1993."
